---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="KoblScribl">
  <section class="home-page">
    <header class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Little Hoard of Stories</p>
      <h2>KoblScribl</h2>
      <p class="hero-text">
        Kobold keep many scribls. Some shiny, some messy, some bite back.
        All kept here, safe in hoard.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button-primary" href="/works">Dig Through Hoard</a>
        <a class="button-secondary" href="/works/originals">Kobold-Made Tales</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="home-section">
  <h3>About the Kobold</h3>

  <div class="about-card">
    <p>
      I write under the names <strong>IshaTheKobold</strong> and <strong>Maxwell’s Daemon</strong>,
      depending on where you’ve found me. This archive is a place for the stories that
      have collected around me over time: fanworks, original pieces, strange little ideas,
      and the occasional thing that grew claws when I wasn’t looking.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most of what I write leans character-first. I’m drawn to stories shaped by
      relationships, worldbuilding, and the moments where people are forced to confront
      themselves, each other, or the worlds they live in. The tone varies, but you’ll
      find a mix of wonder, emotional weight, moral testing, and the occasional sharp edge.
    </p>

    <p>
      Some works here include mature themes, emotional heaviness, and NSFW content.
      Anything important should be tagged where it matters, though some stories do have
      a habit of wandering into darker corners than expected. Any stories marked as NSFW, 
      please ensure you are of legal age in your location before reading.
    </p>

    <p>
      Think of this as a somewhat organized hoard of scribbles. I can’t promise every
      piece will be for you, but I do hope you find something here worth carrying away.
    </p>

    <p class="about-closing">
      If not, well. The hoard keeps growing anyway.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <h3>What in Hoard?</h3>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <article class="info-card">
          <h4>Fan-Scribls</h4>
          <p>
            Stories from other worlds. Kobold borrow shiny ideas, make new shinies.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="info-card">
          <h4>Cross-Scribls</h4>
          <p>
            Two worlds smash together. Sometimes works. Sometimes explodes. Always interesting.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="info-card">
          <h4>True Kobold Tales</h4>
          <p>
            Original stories. No borrowing. All hoard-made.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <h3>Where Dig?</h3>

      <div class="browse-grid">
        <a class="browse-card" href="/works">
          <span class="browse-title">Whole Hoard</span>
          <span class="browse-text">Everything piled together. Careful where you step.</span>
        </a>

        <a class="browse-card" href="/works/crossovers">
          <span class="browse-title">Cross-Scribls</span>
          <span class="browse-text">Worlds tangled up in strange ways.</span>
        </a>

        <a class="browse-card" href="/works/originals">
          <span class="browse-title">Kobold Originals</span>
          <span class="browse-text">Stories born in this hoard alone.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .home-page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #cfc7bb;
  }

  .hero h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero-text {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 60ch;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .button-primary,
  .button-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.65rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
  }

  .button-primary {
    background: #1d1d1d;
  }

  .button-secondary {
    background: #151515;
  }

  .button-primary:hover,
  .button-secondary:hover {
    background: #202020;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .home-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .home-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-grid,
  .browse-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .info-card,
  .browse-card {
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    background: #151515;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .info-card h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .info-card p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .browse-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .browse-card:hover {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .browse-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .browse-text {
    color: #cfc7bb;
  }

  .about-card {
  border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
  background: #151515;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  padding: 1.25rem;
}

.about-card p {
  margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
}

.about-card p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.about-closing {
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.9;
}
</style>